Para sa posisyon ng High Priest
ng High Priest's Office,

00:14:01.170 --> 00:14:02.750
mayroon ka bang angkop na kandidato?

00:14:02.750 --> 00:14:04.120
Ang Mahistrado ng West Market, Kang Yuanli,

00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:05.030
ay tapat at dedikado,

00:14:05.030 --> 00:14:06.360
na may mahusay na reputasyon.

00:14:06.360 --> 00:14:07.550
Maaari siyang itaas sa Punong Pari

00:14:07.550 --> 00:14:09.960
at patuloy na maglingkod bilang
Mahistrado ng West Market.

00:14:09.960 --> 00:14:11.120
Parang bagay sa akin.

00:14:11.120 --> 00:14:12.600
Ipalabas sa Ministry of Personnel
ang utos.

00:14:12.600 --> 00:14:13.150
Oo.

00:14:16.150 --> 00:14:17.080
Xiong Qiannian.

00:14:17.150 --> 00:14:19.600
Sa mga ganitong insidente na naganap sa Chang'an,

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:22.600
ano ang iyong pananaw
bilang Chief Administrator ni Yongzhou?

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:23.800
kamahalan,

00:14:24.480 --> 00:14:26.290
Nabigo ako sa aking pamamahala

00:14:26.550 --> 00:14:27.350
at nagkasala ako.

00:14:28.080 --> 00:14:29.360
Guilty talaga!

00:14:31.400 --> 00:14:32.870
Matagal ka nang nasa Nanzhou Prefecture

00:14:32.870 --> 00:14:34.960
at ilang araw lang nakabalik sa kapitolyo .

00:14:34.960 --> 00:14:36.480
